Sub-clause 4 of Regulation 8 reads as follows :
"Reg. 8(4) The Bureau RC shall invite comments/recommendations on the applications referred to in sub-regulation (3) from the follow-ing, namely :
(i) the State Government concerned ;
(ii) the affiliating University/State Board of Technical Education;
(iii) Bureaus MPCD;
(iv) Bureau BOS;
(v) Bureau RA;
(vi) the Regional Office."
